Package: metaDEA
Type: Package
Title: Perform co-DE gene analysis
Description: Perform a meta-analysis of gene expression data, integrating the results of different differential expression analysis. Subset a list of differential expression analyses based on fold changes and p-values. Find gene statistics and find and plot the most consistent co-differentially expressed genes across the comparisons.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ilario De Toma
Maintainer: Ilario De Toma <idetoma@imim.es>
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Encoding: UTF-8
